text: Marthe Armelle Bilée Etoga (born 3 May 1989) is a Cameroonian national volleyball player. She played at the 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for Bafia Evolution. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Cameroonian sportspeople Category:Volleyball players
